        %h1.mt-4.text-2xl.tracking-tight.text-gray-900.font-serif
          Preparing your Deal ✨
        %p.mt-6.text-base.leading-7.text-gray-600
          Feel free to grab a coffee while we handle this for you! We'll notify you when it's ready.

        %div.border.border-gray-300.rounded-md.shadow-md.bg-white.p-6.text-center.mt-10
          %div.flex.flex-col.justify-center.items-center
            %svg.animate-spin.-ml-1.mr-3.h-10.w-10.text-white{fill: "none", viewbox: "0 0 24 24", xmlns: "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"}
